        "subject": "LU-9414 ptlrpc: rpc hung on ENOMEM in LNetMDAttach",
        "message": "LU-9414 ptlrpc: rpc hung on ENOMEM in LNetMDAttach\n\ncommit 7571f2b4ef59d8ec42c320e08d346cd9c6447f4b\nLU-6356 ptlrpc: do not sleep if encpool reached max capacity\n\nuses ENOMEM for special request handling,\nit is needed to check for rq_sent to distinguish it from\nreal ENOMEM.\n\nSet unlinked flags if request failed to attach to not\nget stuck in the unregistering state.\n\nChange-Id: Idefe820cc1174f80579a873d563bf246c1c7967a\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-4325\nSigned-off-by: Andriy Skulysh <andriy.skulysh@seagate.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
